M|Clos|tx|```
M|Clos|tx|</Bad>
M|Clos|tx|<Good>
M|Clos|tx|```markdown
M|Clos|tx|Write code before tst? dl it. Start over.
M|Clos|**No|**
M|Clos|it|Don't keep it as "reference"
M|Clos|it|Don't "adapt" it while writing tests
M|Clos|it|Don't look at it
M|Clos|it|dl means dl
M|Clos|tx|```
M|Clos|tx|</Good>
