M|The |tx|**Creating skills IS TDD for process doc.**
M|The |Same|No skill w/o failing tst first.
M|The |Same|RED (baseline) → GREEN (write skill) → rf (close loopholes).
M|The |Same|Better qual, fewer surprises, bulletproof results.
M|The |tx|If you follow TDD for code, follow it for skills. It's the same discipline applied to doc.